{"type":null,"faqId":31868,"title":"为什么别的蓝牙设备无法检测到我的蓝牙？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>可能有以下原因：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>未开启蓝牙可检测性。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>您可以在蓝牙设置界面，点击或滑动“开放检测”后的开关至“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98990\" style=\"width:0.28541666in;height:0.20625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，使您的手机可以被别的设备检测到。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">图1-1</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98991\" style=\"width:5.16875in;height:3.7256944in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n <span>蓝牙可检测性超时。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>您可以在蓝牙设置界面，点击 “菜单 &gt; 检测超时设置”，点击选择蓝牙可被检测到的时长并同时开启可检测性。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">图1-2</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98992\" style=\"width:5.16875in;height:3.7256944in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98993\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6388","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1435287940000,"seriesProductName":"DAV-703L","visitedTimes":54,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"蓝牙,蓝牙检测,bluetooth","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}